Apparently part of the firey avenger quest is in here. A paladin in the plane of air asks for the head of miragul and the robe of miragul, at least one of which can be found on the liche of miragul in this zone.Anyone have any more information?(You can read some more on this at Allakhazam's magical realm, don't remember the address, sorry)<br><br>
